700902f-a.title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Sexton Place
700902f-a.text:
East Gunhill Road, south side, east from Sexton to Dewitt Places,
showing the railroad station of the New York, Westchester and Boston
Railroad.
Jumne 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
